data.description: This awesome 3 bed/2 bath brick home sits on a quarter acre corner lot in a quiet neighborhood just inside the loop with a large fenced in yard and a patio that overlooks the whole neighborhood.  It is only blocks away from Coston Elementary school and only minutes from the middle school and the high school. The master bedroom has a walk in closet and en suite bathroom. This hidden gem boasts a bonus room with a large sliding glass door that looks out onto the patio, built in book shelves, a laundry room with tons of extra cabinet space, and a large storage shed in the backyard. It is equipped with a sprinkler system and double hung hurricane glass windows and screens throughout that come with a lifetime warranty. Other notable details include a new roof replaced only 7 years ago and high quality insulation installed less than 3 years ago.
